metadata.name: 1. World in Hiatus
metadata.description:
Title : World in Hiatus  
Artist : Sachie Nagasawa  
Date : 15th March 2020  
Series : Elapsing Time Diary  
Token : #1  
Resolution : 4500 x 6000

A photographic diary of the first lockdown from March 15 to June 2, during which I photographed every day, of this extraordinary ordinary life. I took the time to observe, for 58 days, time passing, slowly but surely, and to live according to its rhythm.
